{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was a life we loved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was the life we knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course, we did go to school in the summer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I need to remind-- say this, that we did go to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In all different parts, wherever we were, what town, city, wherever-- if it was for three days, it was for two days, we went to school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had a book, and it had to be signed by the principals in each particular town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it just had to all harmonize together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We weren't missing any school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because that's the only way my parents could take us out of school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's how we were raised.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then we had our steady schooling in the fall, when we got home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Home was Biedenkopf.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we are at [GERMAN], a steady home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad had bought a home before I even was born there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think they had four or five children when they bought that house, and we just grew up in that house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I left Germany, I went to the United States, that [GERMAN] was there, my family still in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Today it's still a Backer house, because my-- one of my nephews bought the place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, going back to the-- the-- the Gypsy life, it's-- it was a wonderful life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I can't say anything else about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it-- it's even alive, it's hard to explain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You really have to live that type of a life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Little artistic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dad was in the weaving business, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] making baskets, fine stuff, furniture.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother had her children, and we were taking care of each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was a good life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had lots of love.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's one thing I have to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Lots of children.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
